title: Command Key not working (Mac)
body:
Hi there,

My command key + 1 is bound to 'level up ability 1' - but it doesn't work. The keybind says it is this, I have tried restoring defaults and re-entering it, but it doesn't work. Instead it just casts the ability/spell.

replies.body: Do you have any key-reading programs installed and running, such as Accessibility options or a third-party shortcut program?
